-Why it matters: guest name persistence is still broken before the first hall order. The edited name is only written to `localStorage` (`menuapp_guest_name`) and never becomes the fallback display name in the drawer. On submit, a new guest is created with `addGuestToSession(session.id, null, deviceId)`, so the persisted name is not attached to the created guest record either. After refresh / browser kill, the user falls back to `Guest` again.
